#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "In Defence of Mountains"
msgstr "À la défense des montagnes"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:55
msgid "26 JUL | Istanbul, Turkey"
msgstr "26 JUILLET | Istanbul, Turquie"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:57
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image18.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image18.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:59
msgid ""
"Rebels from XR Turkey joined [hundreds of protestors in "
"Istanbul](https://twitter.com/yokolus_isyani/status/1287450564217929728?s%3D21) "
"to condemn theviolent arrest of environmental activists trying to reach "
"Mount Idato protect it from mining."
msgstr ""
"Des rebelles de XR Turquie ont rejoint [des centaines de manifestants à "
"Istanbul](https://twitter.com/yokolus_isyani/status/"
"1287450564217929728?s%3D21) pour dénoncer l'arrestation violente "
"d'activistes environnementaux qui avaient tenté d'atteindre le Mont Idato "
"pour le protéger de l'exploitation minière."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:61
msgid ""
"The mountain has been devastated by a Canadian gold mine which has raised "
"hundreds of thousands of trees and used cyanide to extract the gold."
msgstr ""
"La montagne a été dévastée par une compagnie d'extraction minière canadienne "
"qui a rasé des centaines de milliers d'arbres, et utilisé du cyanure pour "
"l'extraire l'or."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:63
msgid ""
"A coach-load of activists from Istanbul were blocked by police and then "
"arrested, while activists in nearby Çanakkale had [their press conference "
"stormed by "
"police](https://www.sozcu.com.tr/2020/gundem/kazdaglari-mucadelesi-anilacakti-eylemler-bir-hafta-sure-ile-yasaklandi-5952725/amp/) "
"for apparently breaching Covid-19 guidelines.Over 20 activists were fined "
"and jailed overnight."
msgstr ""
"Un bus de militants d'Istanbul a été bloqué par la police, qui les a "
"arrêtés, et dans la ville voisine de Çanakkale [leur conférence de presse a "
"été littéralement prise d'assaut par la police](https://www.sozcu.com.tr/"
"2020/gundem/kazdaglari-mucadelesi-anilacakti-eylemler-bir-hafta-sure-ile-yasa"
"klandi-5952725/amp/), soi disant pour non-respect des normes COVID. Plus de "
"20 d'entre eux ont été condamnés à des amendes, et ont passé la nuit au "
"poste."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:65
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image7.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image7.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:67
msgid ""
"Police storm an Ekoloji Birliği (Union of Ecology) press conference in "
"Çanakkale Photo: SÖZCÜ"
msgstr ""
"Prise d'assaut d'une conférence de presse de Ekoloji Birliği (Union of "
"Ecology) par la police à Çanakkale Photo de : SÖZCÜ"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:69
msgid ""
"Last year the mine was the site of [huge "
"protests](https://twitter.com/KazDagSavunmasi/status/1291053094378364931?s%3D20)."
msgstr ""
"Il y a eu [d'énormes actions de protestation](https://twitter.com/"
"KazDagSavunmasi/status/1291053094378364931?s%3D20) sur le site de la mine "
"l'année dernière."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:71
msgid ""
"A small group of those protestors have stayed on the mountain ever since, "
"[using "
"drones](https://twitter.com/KazdaglarK/status/1263150220914962434?s%3D20) to "
"check the gold mine doesn’t restart operations. Authorities have fined them "
"for their ‘illegal accommodation’ to the tune of thousands of dollars - but "
"the protestors remain. The arrested activists had intended to join them to "
"mark the 1st anniversary of those original protests."
msgstr ""
"Un petit groupe de ces opposants était resté sur la montagne depuis, ["
"utilisant des drones](https://twitter.com/KazdaglarK/status/"
"1263150220914962434?s%3D20) pour s'assurer que la mine d'or ne réouvre pas. "
"Les autorités les ont condamnés à une amende de plusieurs milliers de "
"dollars pour \"occupation illégale\", mais le petit groupe est toujours là. "
"Les militants arrêtés avaient dans l'intention de les rejoindre pour "
"célébrer le premier anniversaire de ce mouvement de contestation."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:73
msgid ""
"A recent report by TEMA, a Turkish environmental group, uncovered that [79% "
"of Mount "
"Ida](http://bianet.org/english/environment/228230-report-on-ida-mountains-79-percent-of-the-region-is-mining-licensed) "
"has been licensed for mining by the government."
msgstr ""
"Un rapport récent de TEMA, un groupe environnemental turc, révèle que le "
"gouvernement a autorisé l'exploitation minière sur [79% du Mont "
"Ida](http://bianet.org/english/environment/228230-report-on-ida-mountains-79"
"-percent-of-the-region-is-mining-licensed)."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:75
msgid ""
"XR Turkey and members of Mount Ida solidarity groups have vowed to not let "
"repression and detentions stop them from defending the mountain."
msgstr ""
"XR Turquie et des membres des groupes solidaires du Mont Ida se sont jurés "
"de continuer à défendre la montagne, malgré la répression et les "
"arrestations."

#. type: Title ###
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "Israeli Rebels Blockade Parliament"
msgstr "Des rebelles bloquent le Parlement en Israël"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:81
msgid "21 JUL | Jerusalem, Israel"
msgstr "21 JUILLET | Jérusalem, Israël"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:83
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image20.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image20.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:85
msgid ""
"In Israel a group of brave rebelsblocked one of 3 roads leading to the "
"parliament,the Knesset, while the other 2 roads were simultaneously [blocked "
"by other "
"movements.](https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-activists-briefly-block-knesset-in-protest-over-law-limiting-government-oversight-1.9011615)"
msgstr ""
"En Israël, un groupe de courageux rebelles a bloqué l'une des trois avenues "
"menant au parlement, la Knesset, tandis que les deux autres rues étaient "
"simultanément [bloquées par des membres d'autres "
"mouvements](https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-activists-briefly-"
"block-knesset-in-protest-over-law-limiting-government-oversight-1.9011615)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:87
msgid ""
"In a remarkable display of non-violent civil disobedience, they physically "
"blocked access to the Knesset to prevent an anti-democratic law from "
"passing, which would reduce parliament’s power to supervise the government’s "
"actions, using the Coronaviruspandemicas a cover. All roads were "
"aggressively cleared by the police. One rebel was arrested."
msgstr ""
"Belle illustration de la désobéissance civile non violente, ils ont "
"physiquement bloqué l'accès à la Knesset pour empêcher l'adoption d'une loi "
"antidémocratique, qui réduirait le pouvoir du Parlement sur les faits et "
"gestes du gouvernement, prétextant la pandémie de coronavirus. Tous les "
"accès ont été brutalement dégagés par la police. Un rebelle a été arrêté."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:89
msgid "Check out our [Unchained](../xr-unchained-17) from XR Israel recently."
msgstr ""
"Voir la rubrique [Unchained](../xr-unchained-17) pour d'autres récentes "
"actions d'XR Israël."

#. type: Title ###
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "Taiwan’s Clean Air Parade"
msgstr "La marche de l'air pur à Taïwan"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:95
msgid "8 AUG| Taichung, Taiwan"
msgstr "8 AOÛT| Taichung, Taiwan"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:97
msgid ""
"On Saturday 8 August, XR Taiwan rebels joined other environmental groups on "
"the streets of Taichung City in central Taiwan, to call on the government to "
"[cut air pollution and coal "
"use](https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2020/08/09/2003741371). "
"The city is home to Taiwan’s largest coal-fired power plant."
msgstr ""
"Le samedi 8 août, Des rebelles d'XR Taiwan se sont joints à d'autres "
"mouvances environnementales dans les rues de Taichung, dans le centre de "
"Taiwan, pour prier le gouvernement de [réduire la pollution atmosphérique et "
"la combustion de charbon](https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/"
"2020/08/09/2003741371). Il y a à Taichung la plus grande centrale électrique "
"à charbon de Taïwan."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:99
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image4.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image4.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:101
msgid "Photo: Su Chin-feng, Taipei Times"
msgstr "Photo de Su Chin-feng, Taipei Times"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:103
msgid ""
"The protestors gathered in front of the city government’s municipal building "
"before setting off on a march. The parade was led by Yeh Guang-perng, "
"chairman of Air Clean Taiwan, and Mayor Lin Shih-hsien, who dressed as "
"[trees to highlight the climate and ecological "
"emergency](https://focustaiwan.tw/photos/20200808ENP0001m)."
msgstr ""
"Les manifestants se sont rassemblés devant le siège gouvernemental de la "
"ville avant d'entamer une marche, derrière Yeh Guang-perng, le président "
"d'Air Clean Taiwan, et le maire Lin Shih-hsien, tous deux déguisés en ["
"arbres pour dénoncer l'urgence écologique et climatique](https://focustaiwan."
"tw/photos/20200808ENP0001m)."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:105
msgid ""
"The Mayordeclared aclimate emergency for the first time in Taiwan.“This year "
"is the most crucial time for people to choose a future of sustainability or "
"extinction,” he told The Taipei Times."
msgstr ""
"\"Cette année sera cruciale. Les gens vont devoir choisir entre un avenir "
"durable ou l'extinction de masse\", a-t-il déclaré au Taipei Times."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:107
msgid ""
"The protestors urged the government to do the same, to promote green "
"policies and shift to a net-zero carbon economy ."
msgstr ""
"Les manifestants ont exhorté le gouvernement à faire de même, à mettre en "
"œuvre des mesures environnementales, et à repenser l'économie à travers le "
"prisme de la neutralité carbone."

#. type: Title ###
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "Indigenous Emergency"
msgstr "Urgence autochtone"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:113
msgid "9 AUG | London, UK, and Worldwide"
msgstr "9 AOÛT | Londres, Royaume-Uni, et dans le monde entier"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:115
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image9.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/newsletter42-image9.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:117
msgid ""
"The steps of Trafalgar Squareturned red with fake blood, and the fountain "
"neon green, as rebels declared an Indigenous Emergency in London. Banners "
"displayed the motto ‘Genocide = Ecocide’, and people painted one hand red, "
"one green, to highlight the plight of Indigenous Tribes in Brazil. Actions "
"also took place in Spain, "
"[Portugal](https://www.instagram.com/tv/CDqwKwanhXR/?igshid%3Defk3am9qfxpg), "
"and the US. Five rebels were arrested."
msgstr ""
"Les marches de Trafalgar Square rouges de faux sang, et l'eau de la fontaine "
"vert fluo, les rebelles déclarent l'urgence autochtone, brandissant des "
"banderoles \"Génocide = Ecocide\". Il s'agissait de se peindre une main en "
"rouge, l'autre en vert, pour symboliser la situation désastreuse des peuples "
"autochtones au Brésil. Cette action a été menée en Espagne, au "
"[Portugal](https://www.instagram.com/tv/CDqwKwanhXR/?igshid%3Defk3am9qfxpg) "
"et aux États-Unis entre autres. Cinq rebelles ont été arrêtés."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:119
msgid ""
"[706 indigenous "
"people](http://emergenciaindigena.apib.info/en/dados-covid-19-novo/) says "
"“We denounce \\[the federal indigenous health service’s] lack of "
"transparency and institutional racism anddemand respect for our rights.”"
msgstr ""
"[706 autochtones](http://emergenciaindigena.apib.info/en/dados-covid-19-novo/"
") déclarent : “Nous dénonçons l'absence de transparence et le racisme "
"institutionnel des servives de santé fédéraux à l'égard des peuples "
"autochtones, et exigeons le respect de nos droits.”"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:121
msgid ""
"Indigenous tribes’ first contact with foreign infectious diseases (including "
"influenza) was during the European colonial invasion in the 15th century, "
"which wiped out92% of the indigenous population."
msgstr ""
"Les tribus autochtones ont été en contact pour la première fois avec des "
"maladies infectieuses étrangères (dont la grippe) lors de l'invasion "
"coloniale européenne au XVe siècle, qui ont anéanti 92 % de la population "
"autochtone."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-24-newsletter-42.md:123
msgid ""
"You can [donate to APIB](http://apib.info/donate/?lang%3Den) so they can buy "
"food, medicine and hygiene materials."
msgstr ""
