msgid ""
"It is the longest river in Poland. It is of great importance in every corner "
"of the country. As children, we sang songs about her and listened to her "
"legends. The [Vistula](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vistula), queen of "
"Polish rivers, is drying up due to climate change and disastrous corporate "
"and human actions."
msgstr ""
